Good-bye, rabbits.

57:14.254 --> 57:15.554
Rabbits?

57:15.556 --> 57:17.024
Hello? Rabbits?

57:17.692 --> 57:19.260
- Rabbits?
- Thomas?

57:20.028 --> 57:21.096
Yeah?

57:22.097 --> 57:24.263
What are you doing
out in the garden so late?

57:24.265 --> 57:25.267
Uh...

57:26.401 --> 57:28.534
I'm picking wildflowers.

57:30.972 --> 57:32.605
It's for you.

57:32.607 --> 57:34.140
He's come back to life.

57:34.142 --> 57:35.676
With a light on his head.

57:35.678 --> 57:37.111
He's evolving.

57:38.245 --> 57:40.282
What were you doing
out in the garden?

57:41.149 --> 57:42.013
Doing?

57:42.015 --> 57:43.251
Yeah. By the tree.

57:44.151 --> 57:46.218
"Doing" can mean
so many things, can't it?

57:46.220 --> 57:48.287
- I mean, I was, I was...
- Would you mind?

57:48.289 --> 57:50.556
- It's just awfully bright.
- I was do... Is it?

57:50.558 --> 57:53.225
Is it distracting you from what
you were asking me just then?

57:53.227 --> 57:54.126
Is it better down?

57:54.128 --> 57:56.198
Up. Up. It's quite bright.

57:56.997 --> 57:59.397
And so we advance to endgame.

57:59.399 --> 58:01.066
You sure you know
what you're doing?

58:01.068 --> 58:03.301
What? We're tryin' to get
our garden back.

58:03.303 --> 58:05.037
