got thrown into a river.

58:52.453 --> 58:53.455
Trust me.

58:56.323 --> 58:57.325
I got this.

59:17.278 --> 59:18.545
Cotton-Tail, go.

59:27.455 --> 59:28.457
Hello?

59:30.224 --> 59:32.759
Ready. Aim. Hold it.

59:32.761 --> 59:34.694
Hold it.

59:34.696 --> 59:36.127
- Thomas.
- Fire!

59:37.533 --> 59:40.500
- Morning.
