59:40.502 --> 59:41.601
Uh...

59:41.603 --> 59:44.102
Yes. That...
Lunch would be lovely.

59:44.104 --> 59:45.672
I was thinking of
making a salad.

59:45.674 --> 59:46.840
Oh, yeah.

59:46.842 --> 59:48.544
