But, really,
you're the oldest,

01:02:28.302 --> 01:02:30.569
and I'm nothing.

01:02:30.571 --> 01:02:32.641
No! Mopsy, don't go.

01:02:33.374 --> 01:02:34.708
Mopsy?

01:02:39.880 --> 01:02:42.949
Hmm? It was just a tomato.
