01:02:42.951 --> 01:02:44.817
Guys, I'm fine!

01:02:44.819 --> 01:02:46.952
It's just a tomato!

01:02:46.954 --> 01:02:49.489
Hey, you never heard
any of that stuff, got me?

01:02:49.491 --> 01:02:50.525
Hmm.

01:02:51.659 --> 01:02:52.791
Dink.

01:03:10.478 --> 01:03:11.878
