I am a nice person.

01:03:22.456 --> 01:03:24.690
I've chilled out, man.

01:03:24.692 --> 01:03:26.024
I'm cool now.

01:03:26.026 --> 01:03:29.695
I've evolved, but you,
you're still the same.

01:03:29.697 --> 01:03:31.697
Still full of mischief.

