01:04:20.915 --> 01:04:21.947
Explosives?

01:04:21.949 --> 01:04:23.015
But you wouldn't do that.

01:04:23.017 --> 01:04:24.082
I wouldn't do
something like that.

01:04:24.084 --> 01:04:25.485
- No, of course not.
- They're angels.

01:04:25.487 --> 01:04:26.619
This is their place
as much as ours.

